              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">磐岩百相·元素汲取</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/26/157749474/f422e67b045b43006341d9b296f52662_4646202396230878872.png",
                "id": "talent13825",
                "key": "磐岩百相",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "磐岩百相"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/26/157749474/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_7790109165268771890.png",
                "id": "talent94333",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/26/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_2628497838066210513.png",
                "id": "talent48383",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span>]</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p>我方对敌方出战角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/26/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2725584088519465613.png",
